!note: This plugin is for personal-use only which means i'm not maintaing it (only if needed)
!note: if you want to improve this you can absolutly fork the [REDACTED] out of it (it's unlicensed!)

This is a (ridiculously) simple Neovim plugin to make temporary notes 

(so now u can discuss that neovim > emacs in neovim and make your point! )
(and it has markdown highlighing so u can look good and make your point! )

Keybindings:
    <leader> + m = New memo
    <ESC>        = Close memo
